mod_winbind v1.0
================

mod_winbind is a ProFTPD module that performs user authentication
to Windows domains using Samba's winbind daemon.

Setup
=====

* tar xvzf proftpd-version.tar.gz
* If you wish to use a newer version of mod_winbind that is not yet included
  with a release version of ProFTPD, download the file mod_winbind.c and:

    cp -f mod_winbind.c proftpd-version/contrib

* cd proftpd-version
* ./configure --with-modules=mod_winbind
* make
* make install
* Enable mod_winbind in your proftpd.conf:

    WinbindEngine on

  To automatically create home directories for your users, also add:

    CreateHome on
